<h2 class="bold font-l">Khan kills Admiral Marcus</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Khan infiltrates the Vengeance, and takes control by killing the ship's captain, Admiral Marcus. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GoryDiscretionShot" class='trope-example-link'>Gory Discretion Shot</a></p>
